140
00:08:31,310 --> 00:08:32,000
Bah!

141
00:08:33,600 --> 00:08:34,440
He's a traitor.

142
00:08:34,720 --> 00:08:35,360
A traitor.

143
00:08:35,360 --> 00:08:35,720
A traitor!

144
00:08:36,600 --> 00:08:37,390
Get lost!

145
00:08:39,600 --> 00:08:40,789
