185
00:09:28,910 --> 00:09:29,480
Right!

186
00:09:30,030 --> 00:09:32,080
The Scroll of Mountains and Seas contains tens of thousands of demons.

187
00:09:32,320 --> 00:09:33,390
If they were released now,

188
00:09:33,550 --> 00:09:34,870
