Uncle.

258
00:12:49,320 --> 00:12:50,000
-Uncle Nan？
-Yi.

259
00:12:53,270 --> 00:12:54,000
Yi.

260
00:12:56,150 --> 00:12:56,670
Uncle,

261
00:12:56,720 --> 00:12:57,150
